"Commercial Use": Any use within the scope of economic activity, including but not limited to: sale, licensing for fee, integration into commercial products or services, use in revenue-generating activities, or use by for-profit entities in their business operations.
"Derivative Work": Any modification, adaptation, translation, enhancement, or other transformation of the Software that incorporates substantial portions of the original code or functionality.
"Distribution": Making the Software or Derivative Works available to third parties through any means, including but not limited to download, physical media, or network transmission.

